<TEXT>
<P>
SHIJIAZHUANG, May 18 (Xinhua) -- The largest foreign economic
and trade fair ever hosted by north China's Hebei Province opened
today in this provincial capital, attracting 400 business people from
more than 40 countries and regions.
</P>
<P>
Hebei has hosted 15 such trade fairs since 1984. The current
fair will feature 933 projects in 15 sectors, including
agriculture, electricity, metallurgy, transportation and
communications.
</P>
