Zhang Jun/Zhang Wei bt Lok Tin Tam/Kwun Yuen Yau 15-2, 15-9
</P>
<P>
Chen Gang bt Kwok Wa Liu 15-0, 15-10
</P>
<P>
(Denmark and China qualified for the semi-finals.) 
