<HEADLINE> Malaysia to Host FPDA Air Defense Seminar </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KUALA LUMPUR, May 18 (Xinhua) -- Malaysia's Defense Ministry
announced Monday a two-day Five Power Defense Arrangement (FPDA)
air defense seminar will be held in Subang near here this week.
</P>
<P>
