<HEADLINE> WTO Ministerial Conference to Discuss Trade Development </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
GENEVA, May 18 (Xinhua) -- Leaders and trade ministers from the
members and observers of the World Trade Organization (WTO) began
here Monday to talk about measures for the further development of
world trade at the second WTO ministerial conference.
</P>
